_content\"]", "pdf": null, "order": 0}, "model": "repo.question", "pk": 85}, {"fields": {"files": [], "lessons": [28], "order_dirty": true, "byline": "", "title": "The scenario: Lotrafiban", "text": "<p>Your company has started a clinical program looking at SB 214857 as a prevention for heart attack and stroke. You have scaled up the medicinal chemistry route, with a few modifications, to make multi Kg quantities of drug substance. Planning for phase III studies, a demand of 3 tonnes (3,000Kg) of API is requested. Do you stick with the current medicinal chemistry route and just scale-up, or do you invest time and resource in a new route? You need to justify your decision.</p>\r\n<p>[figure: lotrafiban]</p>", "remote_id": 341, "dirty": "[]", "pdf": null, "order": 1}, "model": "repo.question", "pk": 86}, {"fields": {"files": [], "lessons": [], "order_dirty": true, "byline": "", "title": "The medicinal chemistry route", "text": "", "remote_id": null, "dirty": "[\"h5p_library\", \"type\", \"h5p_resources\", \"json_content\"]", "pdf": null, "order": 0}, "model": "repo.question", "pk": 87}, {"fields": {"files": [1245], "lessons": [28], "order_dirty": true, "byline": "", "title": "The scenario: the manufacturing route", "text": "", "remote_id": 343, "dirty": "[]", "pdf": null, "order": 3}, "model": "repo.question", "pk": 88}, {"fields": {"files": [1246], "lessons": [28], "order_dirty": true, "byline": "", "title": "The scenario: demands on the process chemist", "text": "<p>In reality, this is not a simple scenario and in industry the process chemist has a number of demands placed on them from different areas of the business.</p>", "remote_id": 344, "dirty": "[]", "pdf": null, "order": 4}, "model": "repo.question", "pk": 89}, {"fields": {"files": [], "lessons": [28], "order_dirty": true, "byline": "", "title": "Worksheets", "text": "", "remote_id": 345, "dirty": "[]", "pdf": null, "order": 5}, "model": "repo.question", "pk": 90}, {"fields": {"files": [1235], "lessons": [28]